[26/06/2018 22:47:33] <font color="#ff00ff">Ahora estoy aprendiendo inglés.</font>
[26/06/2018 22:47:34] <font color="#ff00ff">Fíjese.</font>
[26/06/2018 22:47:37] <font color="#ff00ff">My name is Ambroise...</font>
[26/06/2018 22:47:40] <font color="#00ff00">¿Y eso qué es?</font>
[26/06/2018 22:47:40] <font color="#ff00ff">Ah, es una broma.</font>
[26/06/2018 22:47:47] <font color="#ff00ff">Y usted, what is your name?</font>
[26/06/2018 22:48:13] <font color="#ffffff">¿Qué desea?</font>
